songs.title: Blueberry Kisses
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah

[Verse 1]
Blueberry kisses
My lips, they miss his, oh, yeah
Where did you go now?
Where did you go?
Blueberry kisses

[Pre-Chorus 1]
I told you baby, I'd love you maybe
But you stopped the clock the second time around

[Chorus]
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
'Round and around
'Round and around, and around

[Verse 2]
Blueberry kisses
The muffin man, he misses them kisses, yeah
Where did they go now?
Where did you go?
Blueberry kisses

[Pre-Chorus 2]
I told you baby, I'd L-O-V you maybe
But you stopped the clock the second time around
Yeah, I know it's crazy
But I've been feeling lately that I need you around-ou-ou-ou-ound

[Chorus]
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
I need you around, 'round, 'round (blueberry kisses)
